column2: select top # h.x, h.y, h.z, h.phkey, h.halfmassradius, sh.* , floor (sh.subhaloid/#) as derived_snapnum , floor ((sh.subhaloid-sh.snapnum*#) /#) as derived_filenr , sh.subhaloid-sh.snapnum*#-#*floor ((sh.subhaloid-sh.snapnum*#) /#) as derived_rank from MR h , MField..fofsubhalo sh where h.snapnum = # and sh.subhaloid = h.subhalofileid and h.np between # and # and h.haloid = h.firsthaloinfofgroupid order by newid ()
